      *
      ** BCL Circular 96/127
      *
     D LIM93           S              1A
     D LVIM93          S              1S 0
      *
      ** Define parameters for call module
      *
     D ZALIGNok        S              1A
     D ZFIELD          S             16A
     D ZADEC           S              1P 0
     D ZADIG           S              2P 0
 
      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ End of D-specs                       ¦
      ** ¦ ==============                       ¦
