      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      ** MAIN PROCESSING
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** Initialization
      *
      ** Reset the error flag to prevent problems on subsequent calls
      *
     C                   RESET                   ErrorFound
     C                   RESET                   ZALIGNok
      *
      ** Move '0' if BCL Circular 96/127 is blanks
      *
     C                   IF        LIM93      = *BLANKS
     C                   EVAL      LIM93      = '0'
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Validation
      *
      ** If the BCL Circular 96/127 is entered,
      *
     C                   EVAL      *IN99      = *OFF
     C                   TESTN                   LIM93                99
      *
     C                   IF        *IN99 <> *ON
     C                   EVAL      ErrorFound = 'Y'
     C                   EVAL      #MSGID     = 'ER32014'
     C                   GOTO      #ERROR
     C                   ENDIF
      *
     C                   MOVEL(P)  LIM93         ZFIELD
     C                   EVAL      ZADEC      = 0
     C                   EVAL      ZADIG      = 1
      *
     C                   CALLB     'ZALIGN'
     C                   PARM                    ZALIGNok
     C                   PARM                    ZFIELD
     C                   PARM                    ZADEC
     C                   PARM                    ZADIG
      *
      ** Input is not valid
      *
     C                   IF        ZALIGNok   = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      ErrorFound = 'Y'
     C                   EVAL      #MSGID     = 'ER32014'
     C                   GOTO      #ERROR
     C                   ENDIF
      *
     C                   MOVE      ZFIELD        LVIM93
      *
     C                   IF        (LVIM93 < 0) OR (LVIM93 > 8)
     C                   EVAL      ErrorFound = 'Y'
     C                   EVAL      #MSGID     = 'ER32014'
     C                   GOTO      #ERROR
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** If an error was found, set the return code appropriately
      *
     C     #ERROR        TAG
      *
     C                   IF        ErrorFound = 'Y'
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn  = 'Error '
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Return
      *
     C                   RETURN
      *****************************************************************
     C/EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      * *INZSR - Program Initialisation routine                       *
      *****************************************************************
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
      *
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
     C                   PARM                    #MSGID
     C                   PARM                    LIM93
     C                   PARM                    LVIM93
